        "left": [
          {
            "id": "3a95be19-b769-413a-8dd5-992628738486",
            "label": "Rules reference",
            "blocks": [
              {
                "id": "4b562424-7d92-4c32-8e86-f951f007d26a",
                "label": "What can you do?",
                "type": "Text",
                "value": "Action rolls:\n\tRoll d20 +modifiers from base animal and/or any relevant \tanimal features (can stack)\n\nCrits:\n \t   1 on the dice = -1 to relevant trauma\n\t20 on the dice = +1 to relevant feature\n\nAction roll targets:\n\t  5\teasy\n\t10\tmed\n\t15\thard\n\t18\tvery hard\n\t20\textra hard\n",
                "meta": {}
              },
              {
                "id": "99ca9b9c-74e7-418b-8f0c-ef2e0ecde00d",
                "label": "Combat, contests &amp; Damage",
                "type": "Text",
                "value": "Combat order: roll d20 +relevant modifiers\nDanger moves: roll d20, \n\t  &gt;10\t: achieve something ridiculous \n\t&lt;=10\t: something disastrous happens\n\nContested rolls\n\tEach rolls d20, highest wins\n\tif atk &gt; def, damage = atk - def\n\tif atk &gt;= def, no damage\n\tif 20 on dice, add status effect\n\nEnvironmental damage\n\tMissed action rolls may incur damage = target - roll\n\nHarmful status effects\n\troll d20 each turn\n\tif &gt;10, no damage &amp; recover\n\tif &lt;= 10, suffer effects;\n\tdamage = 10 + status effect modifier - roll\n",
                "meta": { "helperText": "Damage is only applied when relevant" }
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "right": [
          {
            "id": "90bc13a7-aaa3-4caa-917a-235b5e4c93cf",
            "label": "Additional rules",
            "blocks": [
              {
                "id": "77dbde30-fa57-4341-b2ec-45a4c78916bf",
                "label": "temporary modifiers",
                "type": "Text",
                "value": "Assist or preparation: (only lasts whilst relevant)\n\t1\t\t-1 to assist &amp; PC suffers trauma\n\t2-9\t\t0, no effect\n\t10-15\t+1 to assist\n\t16-19\t+2 to assist\n\t20+\t\t+3 to assist\n\nHealing or buff: (buffs expire upon rolling &lt;10 on the dice)\n\t1\t\tPC suffers related trauma\n\t2-9\t\t0, no effect\n\t10-15\t-1 to heal/buff\n\t16-19\t-2 to heal/buff\n\t20+\t\t-3 to heal/buff\n\nApply harmful status effect: (expires upon target rolling &gt;10)\n\t1\t\tPC suffers effect as trauma\n\t2-9\t\t0, no effect\n\t10-15\t-1 to target\n\t16-19\t-2 to target\n\t20+\t\t-3 to target\n",
                "meta": {
                  "helperText": "Always add relevant animal modifiers to rolls applying temporary effects"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "26576995-24e3-489d-869a-57e86c9a5f63",
                "label": "Brute force",
                "type": "Text",
                "value": "A hard (15) obstacle may be passed by 2x (10)\nA very hard (18) obstacle may be passed by 2x (15) or 3x (10)\n",
                "meta": {
                  "helperText": "Some obstacles may be overcome by continual rolling but narratively time must pass between actions"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
